791
01:00:20,610 --> 01:00:22,350
I want to thank you too.

792
01:00:26,900 --> 01:00:30,380
Thank you, Sir Military Prosecutor.

793
01:00:31,460 --> 01:00:33,110
Get going then.

794
01:00:35,280 --> 01:00:36,840
Let's go.

795
01:00:45,450 --> 01:00:48,210
- Let's go.
- Okay.

796
01:00:48,210 --> 01:00:50,980
Hey, when did you get here?

797
01:00:51,690 --> 01:00:53,950
- Did you watch the trial?
- Yes.

798
01:00:53,950 --> 01:00:57,240
Good job. You looked cool, Prosecutor Cha.

799
01:00:58,250 --> 01:01:02,090
But how did No Hwa Yeong's adjutant come out as a witness?

800
01:01:02,090 --> 01:01:04,060
Oh, that.

801
01:01:04,980 --> 01:01:07,020
How do I explain this.

802
01:01:07,020 --> 01:01:10,420
I'm busy, so I'll have to get going. You can explain next time.

803
01:01:10,420 --> 01:01:14,580
Oh, I'm dealing with the company. So don't worry.

804
01:01:14,580 --> 01:01:18,580
Okay. Let me know if you need anything.

805
01:01:18,580 --> 01:01:22,020
What about the hardware? Did you find anything?

806
01:01:27,220 --> 01:01:28,870
That...

807
01:01:30,120 --> 01:01:32,400
It was beyond recovery.

808
01:01:32,400 --> 01:01:35,580
- I disposed of it.
- Are you sure you checked it thoroughly?

809
01:01:37,940 --> 01:01:40,220
I appreciate your efforts, CEO Kang.

810
01:01:40,220 --> 01:01:42,000
I'll go now.

811
01:01:45,050 --> 01:01:48,820
The military court found Corps Commander Hong Mu Seop guilty of abuse of authority and assault.

812
01:01:48,820 --> 01:01:52,690
They punished him severely for both charges.

813
01:01:52,690 --> 01:01:57,130
He will be indicted for the additional charges of sexual assault that came to light during the trial.

814
01:01:57,130 --> 01:01:59,320
Corps Commander Hong...

815
01:02:01,560 --> 01:02:04,390
Power is such an interesting thing.

816
01:02:04,390 --> 01:02:09,220
It takes decades to climb up the ladder, but falling off from it is instant.

817
01:02:09,220 --> 01:02:11,240
How could you...

818
01:02:11,850 --> 01:02:15,370
do this to me? Without any warning.

819
01:02:15,370 --> 01:02:19,570
It's a reward I'm giving to my adjutant who has been loyal to me like you have been. So you should move on.

820
01:02:19,570 --> 01:02:21,200
This time, you should move on.

821
01:02:21,200 --> 01:02:25,400
Don't tell me you didn't do anything about Do Bae Man and Cha Wu In

822
01:02:25,400 --> 01:02:28,770
because you wanted to get rid of Corps Commander Hong.

823
01:02:31,610 --> 01:02:35,240
They say you need two things for a revolution.

824
01:02:36,970 --> 01:02:39,910
Passion and boldness.

825
01:02:39,910 --> 01:02:45,090
I used Do Bae Man and Cha Wu In as a tool to get rid of Hong Mu Seop.

826
01:02:45,690 --> 01:02:48,980
Is there anything I lost from this?

827
01:02:48,980 --> 01:02:51,720
Power doesn't allow a vacuum.

828
01:02:51,720 --> 01:02:55,400
Once there's a vacuum, it will be filled by someone.

829
01:02:55,400 --> 01:02:59,050
I always knew you wanted the position of corps commander,

830
01:02:59,050 --> 01:03:02,240
but I didn't think you'd use this method.

831
01:03:02,240 --> 01:03:04,160
Corps Commander?

832
01:03:05,330 --> 01:03:06,910
That petty position?

833
01:03:07,610 --> 01:03:09,240
General.

834
01:03:14,130 --> 01:03:18,490
Do you know why we didn't clash all this time?

835
01:03:18,490 --> 01:03:23,630
It's because I did everything in my power to not cross the line.

836
01:03:56,310 --> 01:03:59,400
Do you have a response to my offer?

837
01:03:59,400 --> 01:04:02,610
One of the items confiscated from me in the search and seizure

838
01:04:02,610 --> 01:04:05,130
must be an SSD hard drive.

839
01:04:06,310 --> 01:04:10,070
- That is my response
- What's in the hard drive?

840
01:04:10,070 --> 01:04:14,340
A fatal blow to No Hwa Yeong.

841
01:04:19,360 --> 01:04:21,470
Your timing is excellent.

842
01:04:21,470 --> 01:04:23,590
I timed it accordingly.

843
01:04:23,590 --> 01:04:26,820
I saw you were backstabbed by No Hwa Yeong in court today.

844
01:04:26,820 --> 01:04:30,330
I didn't expect you to bring me a present too, CEO Kang.

845
01:04:35,400 --> 01:04:37,620
As you mentioned,

846
