848
01:04:52,210 --> 01:04:54,060
- Yes?
- Hello?

849
01:04:54,060 --> 01:04:57,370
You'll see it right after you pass the infirmary.

850
01:04:57,370 --> 01:05:00,440
Yes, okay. Thank you.

851
01:05:01,770 --> 01:05:04,020
What's going on?

852
01:05:04,020 --> 01:05:06,540
Since when did we have so many phones?

853
01:05:06,540 --> 01:05:12,200
We used to have one but I increased it to five. It was all prepared for this moment.

854
01:05:12,200 --> 01:05:15,940
Wait, what? Hello? Let me fix this.

855
01:05:15,940 --> 01:05:19,350
It's crazy right now. We're getting all sorts of reports on abuse of authority from all across the nation.

856
01:05:19,350 --> 01:05:22,200
The Protectors of Military Human Rights website is down too.

857
01:05:22,200 --> 01:05:26,730
Excuse me. Could you both go into the office? You're bothering us.

858
01:05:26,730 --> 01:05:29,990
Okay, all right. Get back to work then.

859
01:05:30,840 --> 01:05:33,340
Yes, of course, Prosecutor Do is here.

860
01:05:33,340 --> 01:05:35,560
Yes, you can tell me.

861
01:05:35,560 --> 01:05:37,130
Okay.

862
01:05:43,420 --> 01:05:45,340
Why did you follow me in?

863
01:05:50,640 --> 01:05:54,950
I'll tell you since the trial is over.

864
01:05:55,790 --> 01:05:59,370
No Hwa Yeong's adjutant attending as a witness.

865
01:05:59,370 --> 01:06:03,880
It was something I had to do as a military prosecutor.

866
01:06:03,880 --> 01:06:08,680
I had to for Staff Sergeant Sin and No Hwa Yeong's adjutant.

867
01:06:09,290 --> 01:06:10,900
However,

868
01:06:11,750 --> 01:06:14,140
as my father's daughter,

869
01:06:15,310 --> 01:06:18,290
