870
01:06:20,140 --> 01:06:23,030
It was tough.

871
01:06:24,510 --> 01:06:31,590
And I'm sorry for not being able to tell Prosecutor Do Bae Man in advance.

872
01:06:31,590 --> 01:06:34,040
- I am deeply sorry.
